# Sanity Check

Execute commands:

1. `git diff HEAD`
2. `git status --porcelain`

Report:
🚨 Issues  
• Brief description

💡 Quick Fixes  
• Actionable improvement

✅ Good  
• What works

🗑️ Remove  
• Unrelated changes

Focus:

- Critical: security, breaking changes
- High: logic errors, performance
- Medium: code quality, maintainability
- Cleanup: unrelated edits

Style: ultra-concise bullets, priority order, actionable only.

description: AI-powered pre-commit sanity check  
